django-portfolio
================

django-folio is a reusable Django app for show information about work projects.  Projects have attributes such as the 
company it was done for, url etc. You can associte images, files (for e.g ehite pager) , videos as well as recommendations with projects as well as categorize (wbsite,logo,illustration) as well as identify 
particular features of a project e.g (skills e.g Grapphics Design,Django or attribute of a project (

This project was forked from https://github.com/howiworkdaily/django-portfolio however, we 
decided change the name since there was another project on pypi with the same name but with a very different focus.


manifest
========

* portfolio contains the reusable django application
* docs contains varied and sundry documentation
* example_project contains an example project using portfolio